name: So I Finally Flew on the Airbus A350...
description:
The newest addition to Calgary's airline lineup is German carrier Eurowings Discover, which is Lufthansa's vacation airline. 

They started seasonal flights to Calgary in August, supplementing Air Canada’s existing flight to Frankfurt, and will stop service for the season at the end of October.

I knew this is one flight I wanted to try while it was still around, but, there’s a bit of a catch.
